	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001289_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1r'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><term type="boat">Pearl</term> 1 1/2 P.M. 10<hi rend="sup">th</hi> March</p>
<lb/><p rend="right">1858</p>
<lb/><p>Dear <persName>Captain Washington</persName></p>
<lb/><p>We are off at last 
<lb/>and with fair prospects 
<lb/>ahead. I am most 
<lb/>thankful to get into 
<lb/>quiet again. We 
<lb/>are all well &amp; 
<lb/>well provided for 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001289_0002"/><!--pb/@n='1v'--> 
<lb/>and I hope by God's 
<lb/>blessing we shall all 
<lb/>do our duty - once 
<lb/>more farewell and 
<lb/>many thanks for 
<lb/>all your polite 
<lb/>attentions<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p rend="center">I am &amp;c</p>
<lb/><p rend="center">David Livingstone</p>
			
</div>
